            "title": "英皇國際澄天本周錄3宗成交   至今套現5.29億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英皇國際全新港島南臨海住宅項目「澄天」已屆現樓階段，項目自上周日(16/2)起3日分別錄得3宗成交，合共套現逾逾1,500萬。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"澄天\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/501x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/CDT_EMPEROR_SOUTHSKY_750.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"澄天\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/501x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/CDT_EMPEROR_SOUTHSKY_750.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">澄天</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">最新一宗成交為昨日(18/2)售出的15樓B室，實用面積287平方呎，屬1房戶型。買家為內地客人，從上海來港到現樓參觀，斥資514.59萬購入單位，成交呎價為17,930，是次入市將作長線投資用途，預計租務回報率可逾4厘。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「澄天」至今沽出 85伙，佔整體項目逾 77%，合共套現逾港幣 5.29億。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14718308-%e8%8b%b1%e7%9a%87%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e6%be%84%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%a8%e9%8c%843%e5%ae%97%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e8%87%b3%e4%bb%8a%e5%a5%97%e7%8f%be5-29%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/CDT_EMPEROR_SOUTHSKY_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 18:25:48",
